\end{equation*}
$$

In this case, C is connected across an ideal voltage amplifier with a gain of $-A$, so $V_{2}=-A V_{1}$. Substituting this, along with (4.136) and (4.137) into (4.138) yields the interesting result,

$$
\begin{aligned}
